      <subfield code="a">1. Users of accounting &amp; financial information -- 2. Corporate financial statements -- 3. Accrual &amp; deferral timing differences -- 4. Financial statement analysis -- 5. Long-term financial forecasting -- 6. Operating budgets -- 7. Cost-volume-profit relationships -- 8. Capital budgeting.</subfield>
